title: Real Football Manager Edition ENG J2ME S60v3 by Dedomil
description:
Choose from the most prestigious clubs and players in the most extensive football management sim.

* All transfers updated for the 2007/2008 season
* 200 clubs and over 4,000 licenced players
* 3 viewing modes during matches, including an extremely realistic 3D engine
* Personalise your formation and give instructions to individual players
* Very realistic, exclusive transfer system
* Make your tactical changes in real time
